/*.png
/src/frontend/dist

# Safety net for daemon cwd-leaked artifacts (dotnet run sets project dir as cwd;
# any code that writes relative paths would land here). ApacheConfig defaults are
# absolute now, but keep this as defence-in-depth so stray artifacts never
# accidentally get staged.
/src/daemon/NKS.WebDevConsole.Daemon/conf/
/src/daemon/NKS.WebDevConsole.Daemon/generated/
/src/daemon/NKS.WebDevConsole.Daemon/logs/
